          </p>
          <div class="flex space-x-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 p-2">
              <span class="sr-only">Email</span>
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
